{"tid":430252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國警告加泰隆尼亞：若宣布獨立 不會得到國際承認","createTime":"2017-10-09T15:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T08:50:15.000Z","uid":62257,"like":7,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5c35934ad7192f58bc3ff0687572721c87e8852c","tid":430252,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/11532/2747718?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F11532%2F2747718%3Ffrom%3Dudn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news&d=9PqFEyek11r748RoE8T%2ByDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=810d3440\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/11532/2747718?from=udn-ch1_breaknews-1-0-news</a><br />\n<br />\n2017-10-09 20:27<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國歐洲事務部長娜塔莉‧洛伊瑟9日警告西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區，如果宣布獨立，不會得到國際承認。<br />\n<br />\n洛伊瑟告訴網路新聞台CNews：「如果宣布獨立，那將是一廂情願的，不會被承認。這場危機必須透過西班牙政治所有層次的對話來解決。」<br />\n<br />\n洛伊瑟並重申歐盟的警告說，加泰隆尼亞一旦獨立，將「自動」離開歐盟，必須重新申請加入。她說，加泰隆尼亞已經享有「相當大的自治權」"},{"pid":"05ae21b63c8f945270aca979bc3a6879c6baed8a","tid":430252,"uid":294,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"巴塞無得去法甲"},{"pid":"555af5eff8057c139f28116049d8b4476e4c66cb","tid":430252,"uid":132038,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"863a2b638017d6379707bd346841618763cc0464","tid":430252,"uid":132038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7681e243c7572cbbd4e1db28b3db9798d98b586f","tid":430252,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"巴塞去英超啦diu"},{"pid":"8746e66243c0ff178698a44eccc2edd8bf2dcc37","tid":430252,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T15:41:19.000Z","msg":"出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d8b0958371a76b115aaab7248fecfa01b7a9be","t